             [Submit Corrections](#)  Thanks to DANi, JW12, Sumema Fatima for correcting these lyrics.
               Follow HUNTR/X (EJAE, AUDREY …   on Bandsintown                 "Golden" is performed by the singing-voice cast of the film "KPop Demon Hunters": singer-songwriter EJAE sings as Rumi, singer [Audrey Nuna](https://www.azlyrics.com/a/audreynuna.html) sings as Mira, and [REI AMI](https://www.azlyrics.com/r/reiami.html) sings as Zoey. They protect the world from demons and plan to seal their universe. The film's producer Ian Eisendrath explained, *"When they do that, the Honmoon — which is sort of the power that watches over us and symbolized as a big circular moon — will turn gold. When that happens, their job is done."* *"In a traditional film musical structure, this is the 'I want' song,"* he added. *"The whole point is 'It's all going to be golden. We want to fulfill our destiny.'"* The song serves as the second single off of the soundtrack to the film.
